ğŸ”¹ Summary

âœ… If you want a quick + reliable method â†’ use MailKit in PowerShell.

âœ… You can then read Gmail with App Password, fetch inbox, and save to CSV.

âš ï¸ If you plan to filter emails or summarize body text, PowerShell is possible but much easier in Python (Streamlit style).



